HEADWORD: Farmstead
<hw>Farm"stead</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A farm with the
building upon it; a homestead on a farm.</def>
<rj><au>Tennyson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>With its pleasant groves and <qex>farmsteads</qex>.</q>
